WEBVTT

00:00:11.510 --> 00:00:13.510
<font color="#090f13" size="23">Win against McQueen at the Takarazuka Kinen!</font>

00:00:14.030 --> 00:00:16.540
I guess I have to give it up.

00:00:20.010 --> 00:00:23.020
Letter of Withdrawal

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:31.074
