00:01:53.720 --> 00:01:55.030
Like this...

00:01:54.090 --> 00:01:59.050
{\an1}Episode 10
 One Day, Without a Doubt

00:01:55.030 --> 00:01:58.030
And then this and that...

00:01:58.030 --> 00:02:00.490
And then I have to do like this, and then—

00:01:59.530 --> 00:02:00.490
Good Luck

00:02:00.490 --> 00:02:01.540
Yeowch!

00:02:01.540 --> 00:02:03.180
A-Are you okay, Kita-chan?!

00:02:03.180 --> 00:02:04.560
Todally fihe...

00:02:04.560 --> 00:02:05.950
Kita-chan, let me see your hand.

00:02:05.950 --> 00:02:07.790
Run at Full Speed

00:02:05.950 --> 00:02:08.190
Thank you, Dia-chan.

00:02:08.190 --> 00:02:11.570
I know the media and the internet 
are saying all kinds of things.

00:02:11.570 --> 00:02:15.170
But I'm sure Teio will be 
glad to have your charm!

00:02:15.550 --> 00:02:18.220
Run at Full Speed

00:02:15.800 --> 00:02:17.830
Yeah. I hope so.

00:02:18.220 --> 00:02:20.720
{\an9}Good Luck

00:02:20.720 --> 00:02:23.850
Sharpening Their Fangs for the Kikkashou
Will the Racing Prodigy Leave the Track Forever...?
The Summer Races to Check Out!

00:02:22.910 --> 00:02:26.540
Damn it! They just write 
whatever they want, huh?

00:02:26.540 --> 00:02:29.270
All they care about is whether 
or not it gets them attention.

00:02:29.270 --> 00:02:32.930
Anyone wanna explain where the hell Teio's 
been for the last two or three days?

00:02:36.450 --> 00:02:39.780
Maybe she got sick of us 
having her do errands?

00:02:40.170 --> 00:02:41.500
N-No way...

00:02:41.500 --> 00:02:43.850
Is this my fault?

00:02:45.450 --> 00:02:48.660
I know just the plan to get her back!

00:02:51.640 --> 00:02:52.920
Huh?

00:02:53.290 --> 00:02:55.130
Huh, what's this?

00:02:55.130 --> 00:02:57.140
Huh, what's this?

00:02:57.550 --> 00:02:59.920
Huh, what's this?

00:02:59.920 --> 00:03:01.700
Huh, what's this?

00:03:01.700 --> 00:03:03.040
Teio-san!

00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:13.030
Guess I'll come back.

00:03:13.030 --> 00:03:16.020
Spe-senpai, you're the only person 
who would for a trap like that.

00:03:16.890 --> 00:03:19.030
I thought it was a good idea!

00:03:19.030 --> 00:03:21.930
Are you not worried, McQueen? About Teio.

00:03:21.930 --> 00:03:25.910
No matter what becomes of Teio, I will 
continue to do what must be done.

00:03:26.900 --> 00:03:28.660
What must be done?

00:03:28.660 --> 00:03:30.120
{\an8}Letter of Withdrawal

00:03:29.090 --> 00:03:34.120
I will remain a top horse girl, 
worthy of Teio's ambitions.

00:03:37.090 --> 00:03:39.050
{\an8}Letter of Withdrawal

00:03:51.940 --> 00:03:55.100
The racers have entered the final straightaway
 with just over 200 meters left!

00:03:55.100 --> 00:03:56.690
Twin Turbo is hanging tough!

00:03:56.690 --> 00:03:58.120
Symptom Dash is running on the outside,

00:03:58.120 --> 00:03:59.830
with Spain Jelutong on the 
inside in third place,

00:03:58.780 --> 00:04:01.110
I can't!

00:03:59.830 --> 00:04:02.320
but Twin Turbo still has a big lead on both!

00:04:01.110 --> 00:04:03.240
Go!

00:04:02.320 --> 00:04:03.860
Twin Turbo is roaring out there!

00:04:05.750 --> 00:04:08.530
Her turbo engines are at full throttle! 
She outruns the rest!

00:04:09.250 --> 00:04:11.540
Twin Turbo has won the race!

00:04:11.540 --> 00:04:13.150
You did it, Turbo!

00:04:13.150 --> 00:04:14.910
She doesn't spare anything
when she sprints.

00:04:14.910 --> 00:04:16.490
Which is pretty in-character, I guess.

00:04:16.490 --> 00:04:19.020
I can't imagine Turbo running any other way.

00:04:19.020 --> 00:04:21.170
This is her first big win in a while.

00:04:21.170 --> 00:04:23.440
Hell yeah! Did you see that, Teio?!

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:25.930
The way your best rival ever, Turbo, runs?!

00:04:25.930 --> 00:04:27.100
Rival?

00:04:27.100 --> 00:04:29.140
Well, there's no rule 
saying she can't <i>say</i> that.

00:04:30.490 --> 00:04:32.620
An unrequited rivalry, huh?

00:04:37.370 --> 00:04:38.360
It's open.

00:04:41.890 --> 00:04:42.820
Teio...

00:04:44.240 --> 00:04:46.490
Can we talk for a bit?

00:04:48.870 --> 00:04:50.450
You're quitting your team?

00:04:50.450 --> 00:04:55.190
Yeah. When I think about not being 
able to run the same way anymore...

00:04:55.190 --> 00:04:56.830
It hurts worse than I imagined.

00:04:57.780 --> 00:04:59.340
Then you won't be racing anymore?

00:04:59.950 --> 00:05:02.940
Since I sprung that one-sided promise on you,

00:05:02.940 --> 00:05:05.230
I thought I should tell you in person.

00:05:06.250 --> 00:05:10.640
I wanna be a strong and cool horse 
girl like you, Symboli Rudolf-san!

00:05:11.730 --> 00:05:12.970
Teio...

00:05:12.970 --> 00:05:16.220
Sorry to bother you with this gloomy talk.

00:05:17.100 --> 00:05:19.310
You've already decided, then.

00:05:19.310 --> 00:05:21.700
Yeah. Thank you for everything.

00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:26.860
H-Hello?

00:05:27.280 --> 00:05:31.170
Hana-san... are you doing anything tonight?

00:05:31.660 --> 00:05:32.680
Fine.

00:05:36.290 --> 00:05:37.540
Last 20!

00:05:37.540 --> 00:05:38.240
I can't!

00:05:38.240 --> 00:05:39.290
I can't...

00:05:39.290 --> 00:05:42.290
Fight, fight, fight, fight!

00:05:42.290 --> 00:05:47.090
Fight, fight, fight, fight!

00:05:42.930 --> 00:05:47.090
Right... I don't have to run anymore.

00:05:47.870 --> 00:05:51.010
Okay, in that case, I'm gonna have fun!

00:05:51.010 --> 00:05:53.260
And it's obvious what the first stop is!

00:05:53.260 --> 00:05:55.930
A honey double, extra thick 
and extra rich, please!

00:05:55.930 --> 00:05:58.520
Okay, one double, extra thick and 
extra rich, coming right up!

00:05:58.520 --> 00:06:00.270
That'll be 1500 yen.

00:06:02.820 --> 00:06:04.780
So good!

00:06:13.530 --> 00:06:15.040
Nailed it!

00:06:19.390 --> 00:06:21.060
It really suits you!

00:06:21.060 --> 00:06:22.540
Y-You really think so?

00:06:22.780 --> 00:06:25.550
Would you like to try this one on, too?

00:06:25.550 --> 00:06:28.220
This color is trending big this summer!

00:06:28.220 --> 00:06:29.930
Really? Let's see...

00:06:30.290 --> 00:06:31.990
Th-That's...

00:06:31.990 --> 00:06:33.680
No, thank you.

00:06:33.680 --> 00:06:35.680
Karaoke

00:06:46.660 --> 00:06:48.690
So cute!

00:06:49.300 --> 00:06:51.100
Never been to a photo booth before.

00:06:52.130 --> 00:06:53.960
Adorable!

00:06:54.950 --> 00:06:56.400
Yeah!

00:07:00.380 --> 00:07:04.350
Man, I did all kinds of stuff!
 What a fun day.

00:07:04.350 --> 00:07:06.430
I wonder what I should do tomorrow?

00:07:13.450 --> 00:07:17.110
Has one day... always been this long?

00:07:31.100 --> 00:07:32.690
Oh, Teio-san!

00:07:32.690 --> 00:07:33.770
Kita-chan?

00:07:34.620 --> 00:07:36.780
U-Um, I want you to have this!

00:07:37.370 --> 00:07:38.870
Good Luck

00:07:39.100 --> 00:07:42.270
It didn't turn out too good, but...

00:07:42.270 --> 00:07:45.370
I want you to run again, so...

00:07:45.370 --> 00:07:47.260
I worked really hard on it!

00:07:48.590 --> 00:07:52.510
Thank you. But I'm sorry, I can't accept it.

00:07:54.760 --> 00:07:55.750
Bye, now.

00:07:56.920 --> 00:08:01.520
Um, becoming like you, 
Teio-san... is my dream!

00:08:02.660 --> 00:08:07.500
Sorry, but you shouldn't. There are 
other girls you should look up to.

