00:16:52.010 --> 00:16:55.010
Tokai Teio Short Performance

00:17:04.110 --> 00:17:06.270
Guys, thank you so much.

00:17:06.270 --> 00:17:08.140
Don't sweat it. Go wrap it up out there.

00:17:08.140 --> 00:17:10.060
It's hard to say this, but...

00:17:10.060 --> 00:17:12.380
Make sure you don't have any regrets, okay?

00:17:17.190 --> 00:17:19.640
Teio-san!

00:17:19.640 --> 00:17:22.540
Aw, come on, stop crying!

00:17:23.830 --> 00:17:27.990
All right, I'm gonna go on now. 
I'll make this the best goodbye ever!

00:17:34.160 --> 00:17:35.960
Teio!

00:17:42.060 --> 00:17:46.060
{\an8}Tokai Teio Short Performance

00:17:49.060 --> 00:17:53.070
Tokai Teio Short Performance

00:17:53.390 --> 00:17:55.380
Thank you all for coming.

00:17:55.380 --> 00:18:01.590
I'm so glad so many people came to see me, 
even though I haven't been running at all!

00:18:03.080 --> 00:18:06.450
I'm pretty sure you all know this,
 but I broke my leg again!

00:18:06.450 --> 00:18:08.320
This was the third time, 
if you can believe it!

00:18:08.320 --> 00:18:09.740
It's almost kinda impressive, huh?

00:18:10.290 --> 00:18:13.180
After so many times, 
I'm practically used to it.

00:18:13.640 --> 00:18:16.190
Or at least, I thought I would be.

00:18:18.180 --> 00:18:19.330
But...

00:18:20.900 --> 00:18:22.060
That's why...

00:18:25.530 --> 00:18:28.830
When it comes to racing... 
I don't think I can...

00:18:32.460 --> 00:18:34.010
I can't...

00:18:34.010 --> 00:18:36.820
Teio-san! I'll be waiting!

00:19:00.950 --> 00:19:04.300
I'll always be waiting to 
see you run again some day!

00:19:04.300 --> 00:19:05.810
Good Luck

00:19:07.220 --> 00:19:08.470
Teio!

00:19:08.930 --> 00:19:11.620
I don't care if this is me 
being self-centered or greedy!

00:19:08.930 --> 00:19:13.270
Teio

00:19:11.620 --> 00:19:13.550
You've gotta run again!

00:19:13.550 --> 00:19:14.310
Trainer...

00:19:14.310 --> 00:19:15.520
Teio! Teio!

00:19:15.520 --> 00:19:17.630
You have to show us the Teio Step again!

00:19:17.630 --> 00:19:19.590
You look your best when on the track!

00:19:19.590 --> 00:19:21.030
Don't let some injury get you down!

00:19:21.240 --> 00:19:22.090
You're not beat yet!

00:19:22.090 --> 00:19:23.380
You're in the process of winning!

00:19:23.380 --> 00:19:24.510
They're right!

00:19:24.510 --> 00:19:25.860
Please, Teio!

00:19:25.860 --> 00:19:27.230
Don't let it end like this!

00:19:27.230 --> 00:19:28.250
Come on, Teio!

00:19:27.490 --> 00:19:29.430
Tokai Teio Short Performance

00:19:28.250 --> 00:19:29.280
Guys...

00:19:34.920 --> 00:19:36.130
How much longer?

00:19:35.150 --> 00:19:38.760
Is there... no hope?

00:19:36.130 --> 00:19:37.390
Six seconds.

00:19:37.390 --> 00:19:38.020
Make it quick!

00:19:38.020 --> 00:19:38.760
Right!

00:19:39.010 --> 00:19:40.840
The stands are left in shock!

00:19:40.840 --> 00:19:42.510
Twin Turbo has gone all-in
 on this outrun effort!

00:19:42.510 --> 00:19:48.510
She has such a huge lead that it's hard 
to estimate the distance at this point!

00:19:48.510 --> 00:19:50.440
Was this part of the performance?

00:19:50.440 --> 00:19:51.520
What the hell?!

00:19:51.520 --> 00:19:53.550
This wasn't part of the program!

00:19:53.550 --> 00:19:55.010
I'll have them cancel—

00:19:53.980 --> 00:19:56.240
It's fine. I gave the authorization.

00:19:56.940 --> 00:19:59.730
I'm sorry. I forgot to tell you.

00:19:59.730 --> 00:20:02.070
Twin Turbo is on the run! 
She's way out in front!

00:20:02.070 --> 00:20:03.820
Her turbo engines are firing
on all cylinders again!

00:20:03.820 --> 00:20:05.710
Entering the third corner and 
she's still accelerating!

00:20:05.710 --> 00:20:07.330
She's letting it all out on the track today!

00:20:07.330 --> 00:20:09.500
Twin Turbo's running like 
a fugitive, in first place!

00:20:09.500 --> 00:20:13.120
Trying to close the distance is the favorite,
 Rice Shower, ready to move into third!

00:20:13.120 --> 00:20:14.160
She's currently in fourth place

00:20:14.160 --> 00:20:19.760
with her defeat of the top horse girl,
 Mejiro McQueen, still fresh!

00:20:16.800 --> 00:20:19.760
Go for it! Turbo!

00:20:19.760 --> 00:20:21.790
But will the Ebon Stayer manage to catch up?!

00:20:21.790 --> 00:20:26.070
Second place, Weiss Stone, is somewhere 
between 1 to 3 seconds behind Twin Turbo,

00:20:26.070 --> 00:20:28.380
with Imperial Thalys in third!

00:20:28.380 --> 00:20:31.640
But we're already seeing Twin Turbo,
 and only Twin Turbo,

00:20:31.640 --> 00:20:33.760
enter the curve of the fourth corner!

00:20:33.760 --> 00:20:35.630
Twin Turbo is still on the run!

00:20:35.630 --> 00:20:37.360
Twin Turbo is still on the run!

00:20:37.360 --> 00:20:39.930
And as we enter the final straightaway, 
Rice Shower is finally closing in!

00:20:39.930 --> 00:20:43.150
But Twin Turbo is passing 
the 200 meter marker!

00:20:43.150 --> 00:20:44.820
Can Rice Shower make up 
the difference in time?

00:20:47.360 --> 00:20:52.480
This is what happens when you don't give up!

00:20:52.480 --> 00:20:54.090
It doesn't look like Rice Shower will reach her!

00:20:54.090 --> 00:20:57.720
Tokai Teio!

00:20:58.800 --> 00:21:00.750
Number 11, Twin Turbo!

00:21:01.000 --> 00:21:05.070
The runaway Twin Turbo pulls it off!

00:21:05.070 --> 00:21:07.420
Eat that... Teio...

00:21:10.830 --> 00:21:11.760
Tokai Teio Short Performance

00:21:13.430 --> 00:21:15.770
Teio-san!

00:21:17.400 --> 00:21:19.830
Well, this is a total mess.

00:21:19.830 --> 00:21:21.140
Yes, it is.

00:21:21.140 --> 00:21:24.050
There's still so much 
I want to learn from you!

00:21:24.050 --> 00:21:25.400
Please, come back!

00:21:25.400 --> 00:21:26.820
We're begging you, Teio!

00:21:26.820 --> 00:21:28.100
We'd miss you too much!

00:21:28.100 --> 00:21:30.490
Please come back! Let's run together again!

00:21:31.430 --> 00:21:32.570
Come on back.

00:21:34.170 --> 00:21:36.250
I'll say it again...

00:21:36.580 --> 00:21:38.590
No matter what happens to you...

00:21:38.590 --> 00:21:42.030
No matter what anxiety or 
difficulties stand in your way,

00:21:42.030 --> 00:21:44.170
I will continue to run...

00:21:44.170 --> 00:21:47.120
So that I can remain the top horse girl.

00:21:48.430 --> 00:21:52.040
But... I might not be able 
to catch up to you anymore.

00:21:52.670 --> 00:21:57.600
Miracles can happen when people 
wish and strive for them.

00:21:57.950 --> 00:21:59.980
I'm sure of that.

00:22:01.070 --> 00:22:06.450
Teio! Teio! Teio!

00:22:03.480 --> 00:22:09.990
Tokai Teio Short Performance

00:22:06.450 --> 00:22:34.580
Teio! Teio! Teio!

00:22:25.290 --> 00:22:28.700
Well, if you're all gonna be like that...
What else can I say?

00:22:29.510 --> 00:22:30.780
Watch me, everybody...

00:22:31.790 --> 00:22:34.060
I'm gonna try again!

